<TEXT>
<P>
When did "Entertainment Tonight" stop being the harmless, fluffy peek behind 
the scenes at the entertainment industry and become the sleazy tabloid monster 
it is today? Example: a recent hard-hitting "Inside Story" dealt with nude 
movie body doubles. Gimme a break! 
</P>
<P>
Patrick Cervantes, Los Angeles 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
