HIRING; WORKPLACE; PUBLIC ACCESS; AFFIRMATIVE ACTION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052189-0211 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 60243 </DOCID>
