retired in 1984, left, and, far right, current UC Irvine Chancellor Jack 
Peltason. KARI RENE HALL; Photo, Lyndon B. Johnson unveils plaque at 1964 site 
dedication ceremony. Looking on are Chancellor Aldrich and Edward W. Carter, UC 
